  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The most breathtakingly accurate gazebo simulation ever conceived.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Finally, experience the raw existential truth of being an octagonal garden structure.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An absurdist 3D platformer based on traditional mechanics. Break free from your artificial habitat and soar through surreal landscapes, blasting obstacles as you navigate a labyrinthine world in search of escape.</p>",
